DRDGold Gets Extension for Publication of Blyvoor Rescue Plan Until Nov. 1

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-17T13:27:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/drdgold-gets-extension-for-publication-of-blyvoor-rescue-plan-until-nov-1.html
DRDGold Ltd. (DRD)  said its 74 percent-
owned unit, Blyvooruitzicht Gold Mining Co., which is seeking a
business rescue in  South Africa , has been granted until Nov. 1
to publish its business rescue plan.  The company commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  